To host this app on your local machine, follow these steps:

    1) Install node.js if not done already
    2) Navigate to backend directory
    3) run npm i
    4) run npm dev
    5) navigate to frontend directory
    6) run npm i
    7) run npm start

Stack used:

    - Frontend
        - React
        - sass (css)
    
    - Backend
        - Vite
        - mysql (database)
        - sequelize (interacting with database)
        - bcrypt (hashing passwords)
        - jsonwebtoken (sessions)

